Use the standard library
This is how to unique_digits of x:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this x's length times:
    Remember that n is item i in x
    Remember that s is tostring of n
    Remember that seen is []
    Remember that ok is yes
    Remember that j is 0
    Do this s's length times:
      Remember that ch is item j in s
      When ch is in seen, then:
        Remember that ok is no
        Leave the loop
      End when
      Add seen to ch
      Increase j by 1
    End do
    When ok is yes, then:
      Add result to n
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know